{"tid":734225,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"濕疹救星？","createTime":"2018-07-08T12:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T13:46:40.000Z","uid":122116,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"93f4f6803bec53c4dd29945f3eb7a47acf5756b9","tid":734225,"uid":122116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T12:36:13.000Z","msg":"我對手爛咗4年到，天氣一熱就嚴重，冬天個陣會自己好翻，依家一直靠搽類固醇搞到皮膚薄晒，好易擦損，呢幾晚開冷氣訓覺對手竟然自己好翻好多，之前睇過好多中醫都冇用，估唔到開冷氣訓就搞掂，之前老母成日不比開冷氣/開一兩日就唔開所以冇發現到<br />\n<br />\n香港濕氣重，開冷氣可以抽濕，咁其實開抽濕機都得？不過開冷氣訓係訓得舒服好多嘅（睡眠質素對濕疹影響好大）<br />\n<br />\n題外話：有次放9日大假，日日打機打通宵生活日夜顛倒，飲食又唔定時，個時對手竟然又係自己好翻，放完假正常翻又再生野完全唔知做咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c90e521d058f009d557ad0b3b80b5d24e4b7dee1","tid":734225,"uid":122116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T12:39:48.000Z","msg":"暗瘡都好似好咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597b0b8fa0995c2aeb26ffc937f0c3ebfacd653e","tid":734225,"uid":176472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T12:42:17.000Z","msg":"內分泌問題"},{"pid":"ae4d03c6abcba7643f308f13c6918a9165ecce91","tid":734225,"uid":82845,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T12:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/204149_4cc55c98c67a855d7d9becad82d7128b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F204149_4cc55c98c67a855d7d9becad82d7128b.png&h=f13acfc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"440a9f90ec0d4b9c4bfa4c2bc29a8102d5c56b40","tid":734225,"uid":4880,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T12:42:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1323893016301599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS1323893016301599&d=Fmtq7n1FPToUltkVEwSsejANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=e7ace2df\" data-auto-link target=\"_b